image_analysis.description: A high-angle, wide-shot photograph of a large, polished reddish-brown (mahogany or lacquered) desk in an office setting. On the desk sits a large silver Apple iMac computer with a wireless keyboard and mouse. To the left of the computer are two beige multi-line office telephones. To the right are a blue United States passport, a clear container holding pens and pencils, a stapler, a tape dispenser, and a pair of eyeglasses. In the background, there is a white leather sofa, a wooden tissue box, a bottle of hand sanitizer, and a white door. The floor is covered in black carpeting. A black office chair is visible in the foreground.
image_analysis.layout: The desk is the central focus, angled slightly. The computer is centered. Objects are arranged around the perimeter of the desk surface.
